Package: CineGrade
Type: Package
Title: Cinematic Color Grading and Style Transfer for Images
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Devdhar", "Patil",
    email = "devdharup22@iitk.ac.in",
    role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extracts cinematic color grades from reference images using
    k-means clustering in LAB perceptual color space and transfers them
    to any target image. Includes a 1-nearest-neighbour centroid-shift
    color transfer algorithm, PCA-based exploration of color style across
    image collections, UMAP visualization of color distributions,
    artistic stylization presets (poster, pixel, anime, noir, vintage),
    color vision deficiency simulation, and an interactive Shiny dashboard.
